'''Fiama Di Wills''' is an Indian [[personal care]] [[brand]] that offers [[shampoo]]s, [[Hair conditioner|conditioner]], bathing bars and [[shower gel]]s. It is owned by [[ITC Limited]], an Indian [[Conglomerate (company)|conglomerate]] with a market capitalization of USD 40 billion and a [[Revenue|turnover]] of USD 8 billion.<ref>{{Cite web|title = ITC Limited - One of the World's Most Reputable Companies|url = http://www.itcportal.com/about-itc/profile/index.aspx|website = www.itcportal.com|accessdate = 2015-11-14}}</ref>

Launched on September 15, 2007, the brand was the second to roll out of ITC’s personal care stable.

